::Battera::

She stepped out of the chamber and looked around.  She saw Feline 
standing there.  She stood there, leaning on the door to the 
chamber.  She took a few careful steps towards Feline. 

Feline::
She walked over to Battera. "Take it easy there. You've had one bad 
wound inflicted."

Battera::
She nodded and leaned on Fefline for support. "Yeah, I don't feel so 
good."

Feline::
She helped Battera onto the table and put Battera into a deep sleep.  
She worked on the abdoninal wound.  She finished and closed up the 
panels.  While Battera was out cold, she turned Battera's head and 
opened the back head panel.  She put the second chip in Battera's 
head. She smiled and closed the panel.  Then she  she woke Battera up.
"How are you feeling?"

Battera::
A little groggy, she came around. "I..I think I'll be ok."  She sat 
up and looked at Feline. "Thank you for all your help."

Feline::
She smiled, "Hey, no problem. Anytime. Now go to your quarters and 
get some rest."

Battera::
She nodded and got off the table. She walked down the hal and to her 
room.  She sat in her chair and open her link. In a xlightly tired 
voice,"Cybershark. I'm ok. I'm in my room. Just be careful love."
